      <title>(Like) Water Off a Taro Leaf</title>
      <link>https://geraldnguyen.github.io/posts/2023/01/water-off-a-taro-leaf/</link>
      <pubDate>Tue, 31 Jan 2023 09:19:42 +0100</pubDate>
      <guid>https://geraldnguyen.github.io/posts/2023/01/water-off-a-taro-leaf/</guid>
      <description>&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:875/0*4K1HzfiMv7YrvpeC&#34;&#xA;    alt=&#34;Photo by Vi Tran on Unsplash&#34;&gt;&lt;figcaption&gt;&#xA;      &lt;p&gt;Photo by &lt;a href=&#34;https://unsplash.com/@kanbi95?utm_source=medium&amp;amp;utm_medium=referral&#34;&gt;Vi Tran&lt;/a&gt; on &lt;a href=&#34;https://unsplash.com/?utm_source=medium&amp;amp;utm_medium=referral&#34;&gt;Unsplash&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/figcaption&gt;&#xA;&lt;/figure&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;The title is loosely translated from a Vietnamese idiom&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;blockquote&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Nước đổ lá môn&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;A popular variation of this idiom replaces “&lt;em&gt;lá môn&lt;/em&gt;” with “&lt;em&gt;lá khoai&lt;/em&gt;” even though there are different types of leaves with the “&lt;em&gt;khoai&lt;/em&gt;” prefix such as “&lt;em&gt;lá khoai lang&lt;/em&gt;” (potato leaves, “&lt;em&gt;lá&lt;/em&gt;” means “&lt;em&gt;leaf&lt;/em&gt;” in Vietnamese), “&lt;em&gt;lá khoai mì&lt;/em&gt;” (Cassava leaves)…&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;blockquote&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Nước đổ lá khoai&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Another variation replaces the taro leaf with a duck’s head&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>AFF Cup needs VAR</title>
      <link>https://geraldnguyen.github.io/posts/2023/01/aff-cup-needs-var/</link>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Jan 2023 09:19:42 +0100</pubDate>
      <guid>https://geraldnguyen.github.io/posts/2023/01/aff-cup-needs-var/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Thailand comfortably beat Vietnam 1–0 on home soil to seal a 3–2 aggregate win and retain the crown for yet another 2 years. Theerathon Bunmathan was voted the most valuable player of the tournament.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;What impressed me most about Theerathon was not his consistent and superb performance but what he said after the match. Theerathon reportedly said that he wanted VAR to be available in future AFF cups because all participating teams are neighbors and should improve their games together instead of committing faults or injuring each other.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
